        "URL": "data:text/html;charset=utf-8,%3C!doctype%20html%3E%0A%3Chtml%20lang%3D%22%22%3E%0A%3Chead%3E%0A%20%20%3Cmeta%20charset%3D%22utf-8%22%3E%0A%20%20%3Ctitle%3EPeeps%20%26%20Fear%3C%2Ftitle%3E%0A%3C%2Fhead%3E%0A%3Cbody%3E%0A%3Cbody%20text%3D%22%23000000%22%20link%3D%22%230000ff%22%20vlink%3D%22%23800080%22%20bgcolor%3D%22%23feff1f%22%3E%0A%0A%3Ccenter%3E%3Ctable%20cellspacing%3D%220%22%20border%3D%220%22%20cellpadding%3D%227%22%20width%3D%22462%22%3E%0A%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20width%3D%2223%25%22%20valign%3D%22TOP%22%3E%0A%3Ch1%20align%3D%22CENTER%22%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%2272%22%20height%3D%22112%22%3E%3C%2Fh1%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%3Ctd%20width%3D%2255%25%22%20valign%3D%22MIDDLE%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Ch1%20align%3D%22CENTER%22%3EFear%20Response%3C%2Fh1%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Ch1%20align%3D%22CENTER%22%3Ein%20Peeps%3C%2Fh1%3E%0A%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%3Ctd%20width%3D%2222%25%22%20valign%3D%22TOP%22%3E%0A%3Ch1%20align%3D%22CENTER%22%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%2272%22%20height%3D%22112%22%3E%3C%2Fh1%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%3C%2Ftr%3E%0A%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%0A%3C%2Fcenter%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Chr%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIntroduction%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20It%20has%20long%20been%20appreciated%20that%20various%20animals%20have%20%0A%20%20developed%20innate%20responses%20to%20stressful%20situations%20that%20may%20increase%20their%20chances%20%0A%20%20of%20survival.%20Included%20in%20these%20behaviors%20is%20the%20exaggeration%20of%20physical%20size%2C%20%0A%20%20a%20strategy%20employed%20by%20various%20animals%20including%20the%20common%20house%20cat%2C%20the%20pufferfish%2C%20and%20the%20ever%20feared%20Siamese%20fighting%20fish.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Ch6%20align%3D%22center%22%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%22162%22%20height%3D%22110%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%0A%20%20Animated%20fish%20courtesy%20of%20the%20UK%20HGMP%20Resource%20Centre%3C%2Fh6%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%20Other%20behaviors%20of%20a%20similar%20nature%20include%20the%20ability%20of%20skunks%20to%20spew%20%0A%20%20foul%20smelling%20nastiness%20at%20enemies%20(a%20response%20which%20fortunately%20has%20not%20been%20%0A%20%20observed%20by%20peep%20scientists%20thus%20far)%2C%20and%20the%20tendency%20to%20exaggerate%20one's%20%0A%20%20own%20intelligence%20(a%20practice%20employed%20multifariously%20by%20insecure%20scientists%20%0A%20%20who%20through%20obfuscation%20and%20transmogrification%20render%20oblique%20the%20perspicaciousness%20%0A%20%20of%20the%20facts%2C%20and%20attempt%20to%20ensure%20utter%20confusion%20through%20pedantic%20pontification%20%0A%20%20and%20verbose%20oration%20in%20order%20to%20maintain%20the%20illusion%20of%20their%20own%20preeminence).%20%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20assess%20whether%20fear%20adaptations%20are%20present%20in%20the%20peep%20population%2C%20%0A%20%20it%20was%20necessary%20to%20find%20a%20stimulus%20that%20elicits%20a%20fear%20response.%20After%20spending%20%0A%20%20hours%20screaming%20obscenities%20at%20peeps%2C%20and%20subjecting%20them%20to%20a%20variety%20of%20scary%20%0A%20%20stimuli%20including%2C%20but%20not%20limited%20to%20KFC%20commercials%2C%20Dr.%20Laura%2C%20and%20a%20full-length%20%0A%20%20Martha%20Stewart%20video%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20investigate%20whether%20peeps%20exhibit%20fear%20responses%20%0A%20%20when%20placed%20in%20enclosed%2C%20brightly%20lit%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Chr%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%26nbsp%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ctable%20width%3D%22100%25%22%20border%3D%220%22%3E%0A%20%20%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Ctd%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMethods%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Finding%20the%20optimal%20test%20environment%20was%20difficult.%20We%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20required%20a%20highly%20controllable%2C%20enclosed%2C%20artificial%20micro-environment%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20in%20which%20we%20could%20precisely%20manipulate%20ambient%20light%20levels%20while%20observing%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20behaviors.%20We%20selected%20the%20General%20Electric%C2%AE%20600%20Watt%20enclosure%20for%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20our%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Ctd%3E%3Cb%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%22288%22%20height%3D%22232%22%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%20%20%3C%2Ftr%3E%0A%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%26nbsp%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%26nbsp%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ctable%20width%3D%22100%25%22%20border%3D%220%22%3E%0A%20%20%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Ctd%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cdiv%20align%3D%22center%22%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%22288%22%20height%3D%22216%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Ctd%3E%3Cb%3EControl%20Procedure%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20To%20assess%20whether%20enclosed%20spaces%20alone%20produce%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20a%20fear%20response%2C%20our%20subject%20was%20placed%20in%20the%20enclosure%20without%20light.%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20We%20were%20unable%20to%20detect%20any%20increase%20in%20size%2C%20as%20shown%20in%20the%20photo%20on%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20the%20left.%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%20%20%3C%2Ftr%3E%0A%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%0A%3Ctable%20width%3D%22100%25%22%20border%3D%220%22%3E%0A%20%20%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Ctd%20width%3D%2259%25%22%3E%3Cb%3EControl%20Part%202%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3ETo%20rule%20out%20bright%20light%20alone%20as%20a%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20fear-inducing%20stimulus%2C%20our%20subject%20was%20exposed%20to%20a%20light%20source%20bright%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20enough%20to%20elicit%20complaints%20from%20our%20neighbors.%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Ctd%20width%3D%2241%25%22%3E%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cdiv%20align%3D%22center%22%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%22288%22%20height%3D%22194%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%20%20%3C%2Ftr%3E%0A%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%26nbsp%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%26nbsp%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ctable%20width%3D%22100%25%22%20border%3D%220%22%3E%0A%20%20%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Ctd%20width%3D%2243%25%22%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%22302%22%20height%3D%22194%22%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Ctd%20width%3D%2257%25%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EExperimental%20Procedure%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EWhile%20neither%20enclosures%20nor%20bright%20light%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20were%20alone%20sufficient%20to%20induce%20any%20observable%20fear%20response%2C%20we%20hypothesized%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20that%20the%20combination%20of%20these%20conditions%20may%20push%20our%20subjects%20over%20the%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20brink%20of%20unbridled%20terror.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20obtaining%20full%20consent%2C%20our%20brave%20volunteer%20peep%20was%20placed%20on%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20calibrated%20puff-o-meter%C2%AE%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%20%20%3C%2Ftr%3E%0A%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%0A%3Ctable%20width%3D%22100%25%22%20border%3D%220%22%3E%0A%20%20%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Ctd%20width%3D%2259%25%22%3EOur%20subject%20was%20enclosed%20in%20the%20600-Watt%20test%20chamber%2C%20and%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20the%20light%20source%20was%20activated%20by%20setting%20the%20chamber%20for%20a%2030%20second%20run%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20at%20%22maximum%20power%22.%20%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Ctd%20width%3D%2241%25%22%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%22288%22%20height%3D%22216%22%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%20%20%3C%2Ftr%3E%0A%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%0A%3Ctable%20width%3D%22100%25%22%20border%3D%220%22%3E%0A%20%20%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Ctd%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%22345%22%20height%3D%22238%22%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Ctd%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3EAfter%2030%20seconds%2C%20our%20subject%20did%20indeed%20demonstrate%20a%20marked%20increase%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20in%20size%20consistent%20with%20fear%20responses%20described%20in%20other%20species.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%20%20%3C%2Ftr%3E%0A%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%0A%3Ctable%20width%3D%22100%25%22%20border%3D%220%22%3E%0A%20%20%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Ctd%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3EOur%20next%20subject%20volunteered%20for%20a%20longer%20exposure.%20Seen%20here%20is%20the%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20dramatic%20fear%20response%20observed%20after%2075%20seconds%20in%20our%20test%20chamber.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3ENote%20that%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20increase%20in%20size%20projecting%20great%20ferocity%2C%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20the%20subject's%20eyes%20dilated%2C%20as%20is%20often%20observed%20in%20fight-or-flight%20responses.%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Ctd%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%22371%22%20height%3D%22274%22%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%20%20%3C%2Ftr%3E%0A%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%0A%3Ctable%20width%3D%22100%25%22%20border%3D%220%22%3E%0A%20%20%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Ctd%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%22305%22%20height%3D%22186%22%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Ctd%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20removal%20from%20the%20test%20chamber%2C%20our%20subject%20exhibited%20a%20compensatory%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20post-stress%20reaction%2C%20possibly%20due%20to%20exhaustion%20after%20the%20intense%20agonistic%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20display.%20(Wow%2C%20he%20looks%20tired!)%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%20%20%3C%2Ftr%3E%0A%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%26nbsp%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EConclusion%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20It%20is%20the%20opinion%20of%20the%20authors%20that%20these%20data%20clearly%20%0A%20%20demonstrate%20an%20adaptive%20fear%20response%20to%20stressful%20stimuli%20in%20the%20peep%20species.%20%0A%20%20This%20response%20likely%20evolved%20in%20order%20to%20intimidate%20potential%20predators%20through%20%0A%20%20the%20awesome%20size%20and%20prowess%20achieved%20in%20a%20frightened%20peep.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%3EPeeps%20may%20have%20evolved%20this%20adaptation%20only%20to%20the%20combination%20of%20enclosed%20%0A%20%20spaces%20and%20bright%20light%2C%20as%20adult%20peeps%20are%20often%20cornered%20on%20shelves%20by%20flashlight-wielding%20%0A%20%20thieves%20looking%20for%20a%20sugary%20treat%20while%20ransacking%20the%20local%20drug%20store.%20Others%20%0A%20%20have%20theorized%20that%20this%20is%20the%20result%20of%20a%20Jungian%20cultural%20consciousness%20dating%20%0A%20%20back%20to%20the%20horrific%20electric-glowing%20ferret%20invasion%20of%20the%20sub-Saharan%20Peep%20%0A%20%20den%20of%201872%20--%20an%20event%20rivaled%20only%20by%20the%20infamous%20200%20gigawatt%20firefly%20infestation%20%0A%20%20of%20the%20Fluffhaven%20caves%20in%20southern%20Italy.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20cannot%20rule%20out%20the%20possibility%20that%20Peeps%20were%20demonstrating%20fear%20%0A%20%20in%20response%20to%20the%20microwave%20emissions%20coincident%20with%20activation%20of%20the%20test-chamber%20%0A%20%20lighting%2C%20this%20notion%20seems%20too%20outrageous%20to%20warrant%20further%20consideration%20%0A%20%20by%20any%20reasonable%20scientist.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22index.html%22%3EReturn%20to%20the%20Peep%20home%20page%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fhtml%3E"
